{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":640,"text":"Here's my thing."},{"time":2560,"text":"Hold on. There I go. Hey."},{"time":6080,"text":"I want to start today --\ntalk about the structure of a polypeptide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9310,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11680,"text":"I get a lot of people asking me,\nin terms of \"Lost,\" you know,"},{"time":15880,"text":"\"What the hell's that island?\""},{"time":17360,"text":"You know, it's usually followed by,"},{"time":20320,"text":"\"No, seriously,\nwhat the hell is that island?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22520,"text":"Why so many mysteries?"},{"time":23800,"text":"What is it about mystery\nthat I seem to be drawn to?"},{"time":27760,"text":"And I was thinking about this,\nwhat to talk about at TED."},{"time":30480,"text":"When I talked to the kind rep from TED,"},{"time":33680,"text":"and I said, \"Listen, you know,\nwhat should I talk about?\""},{"time":36400,"text":"He said, \"Don't worry about it.\nJust be profound.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":38800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40120,"text":"And I took enormous comfort in that."},{"time":41880,"text":"So thank you, if you're here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43520,"text":"I was trying to think,\nwhat do I talk about? Good question."},{"time":46360,"text":"Why do I do so much\nstuff that involves mystery?"},{"time":48640,"text":"And I started trying to figure it out."},{"time":50520,"text":"And I started thinking\nabout why do I do any of what I do,"},{"time":53280,"text":"and I started thinking\nabout my grandfather."},{"time":55400,"text":"I loved my grandfather."},{"time":57200,"text":"Harry Kelvin was his name,\nmy mother's father."},{"time":60320,"text":"He died in 1986. He was an amazing guy."},{"time":63080,"text":"And one of the reasons he was amazing:"},{"time":64959,"text":"After World War II,\nhe began an electronics company."},{"time":67412,"text":"He started selling surplus parts,\nkits, to schools and stuff."},{"time":72000,"text":"So he had this incredible curiosity."},{"time":73800,"text":"As a kid, I saw him come over to me"},{"time":75720,"text":"with radios and telephones\nand all sorts of things."},{"time":78160,"text":"And he'd open them up, he'd unscrew them\nand reveal the inner workings --"},{"time":81640,"text":"which many of us,\nI'm sure, take for granted."},{"time":83800,"text":"But it's an amazing gift to give a kid."},{"time":86400,"text":"To open up this thing\nand show how it works"},{"time":89000,"text":"and why it works and what it is."},{"time":90640,"text":"He was the ultimate\ndeconstructor, in many ways."},{"time":93640,"text":"And my grandfather was a kind of guy\nwho would not only take things apart,"},{"time":99920,"text":"but he got me interested\nin all sorts of different odd crafts,"},{"time":103200,"text":"like, you know, printing,\nlike the letter press."},{"time":106360,"text":"I'm obsessed with printing."},{"time":107760,"text":"I'm obsessed with silk-screening\nand bookbinding and box making."},{"time":111240,"text":"When I was a kid, I was always,\nlike, taking apart boxes and stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115520,"text":"And last night in the hotel,\nI took apart the Kleenex box."},{"time":118280,"text":"I was just looking at it.\nAnd I'm telling you --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122080,"text":"It's a beautiful thing. I swear to God."},{"time":124000,"text":"I mean, when you look at the box\nand you sort of see how it works."},{"time":127160,"text":"Rives is here, and I met him\nyears ago at a book fair;"},{"time":129759,"text":"he does pop-up books."},{"time":131000,"text":"And I'm obsessed\nwith engineering of paper."},{"time":133080,"text":"The scoring of it, the printing of it,"},{"time":134960,"text":"where the thing gets glued,\nthe registration marks for the ink."},{"time":137960,"text":"I just love boxes."},{"time":139200,"text":"My grandfather was the guy"},{"time":140480,"text":"who kind of got me\ninto all sorts of these things."},{"time":143280,"text":"He would also supply me with tools."},{"time":145000,"text":"He was this amazing encourager --\nthis patron, sort of, to make stuff."},{"time":150600,"text":"And he got me a Super 8 camera\nwhen I was 10 years old."},{"time":154160,"text":"And in 1976, that was sort of an anomaly,"},{"time":156680,"text":"to be a 10-year-old kid\nthat had access to a camera."},{"time":159680,"text":"And you know, he was so generous;\nI couldn't believe it."},{"time":163320,"text":"He wasn't doing it\nentirely without some manipulation."},{"time":166800,"text":"I mean, I would call him, and I'd be like,"},{"time":168840,"text":"\"Listen, Grandpa,\nI really need this camera."},{"time":171400,"text":"You don't understand.\nThis is, like, I want to make movies."},{"time":174200,"text":"I'll get invited to TED one day --\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":176600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177640,"text":"And, you know, my grandmother\nwas the greatest."},{"time":179880,"text":"Because she'd be like, you know --\nshe'd get on the phone."},{"time":182640,"text":"She'd be like, \"Harry,\nit's better than the drugs."},{"time":186360,"text":"She was fantastic."},{"time":188348,"text":"So I found myself getting this stuff,\nthanks to her assist,"},{"time":191600,"text":"and suddenly, you know,"},{"time":192880,"text":"I had a synthesizer\nwhen I was 14 years old --"},{"time":196000,"text":"this kind of stuff."},{"time":197240,"text":"And it let me make things,\nwhich, to me, was sort of the dream."},{"time":201320,"text":"He sort of humored my obsession\nto other things too, like magic."},{"time":204880,"text":"The thing is, we'd go\nto this magic store in New York City"},{"time":207640,"text":"called Lou Tannen's Magic."},{"time":209040,"text":"It was this great magic store."},{"time":210520,"text":"It was a crappy\nlittle building in Midtown,"},{"time":212560,"text":"but you'd be in the elevator,\nthe elevator would open --"},{"time":215240,"text":"there'd be this little, small magic store."},{"time":217320,"text":"You'd be in the magic store.\nAnd it was a magical place."},{"time":220000,"text":"So I got all these magic tricks.\nHere. I'll show you."},{"time":222520,"text":"This is the kind of thing.\nSo it would be like, you know."},{"time":225400,"text":"Which is good, but now I can't move."},{"time":227240,"text":"Now, I have to do\nthe rest of the thing like this."},{"time":229680,"text":"I'm like, \"Oh, wow.\nLook at my computer over there!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":232160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234400,"text":"So one of the things\nthat I bought at the magic store was this:"},{"time":237800,"text":"Tannen's Mystery Magic Box."},{"time":239600,"text":"The premise behind the Mystery\nMagic Box was the following:"},{"time":242400,"text":"15 dollars buys you\n50 dollars worth of magic."},{"time":247080,"text":"Which is a savings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250200,"text":"Now, I bought this decades ago\nand I'm not kidding."},{"time":252640,"text":"If you look at this,\nyou'll see it's never been opened."},{"time":255280,"text":"But I've had this forever."},{"time":257440,"text":"Now, I was looking at this,"},{"time":258800,"text":"it was in my office,\nas it always is, on the shelf,"},{"time":261240,"text":"and I was thinking,\nwhy have I not opened this?"},{"time":264640,"text":"And why have I kept it?"},{"time":266640,"text":"Because I'm not a pack rat."},{"time":268000,"text":"I don't keep everything,"},{"time":269240,"text":"but for some reason\nI haven't opened this box."},{"time":271440,"text":"And I felt like there was\na key to this, somehow,"},{"time":273800,"text":"in talking about something at TED\nthat I haven't discussed before,"},{"time":277200,"text":"and bored people elsewhere."},{"time":279440,"text":"So I thought, maybe\nthere's something with this."},{"time":281720,"text":"And there was this giant question mark."},{"time":283640,"text":"I love the design,\nfor what it's worth, of this thing."},{"time":286200,"text":"And I started thinking,\nwhy haven't I opened it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":288480,"text":"And I realized that I haven't opened it"},{"time":290400,"text":"because it represents\nsomething important -- to me."},{"time":293000,"text":"It represents my grandfather."},{"time":295360,"text":"Am I allowed to cry at TED?"},{"time":296760,"text":"Because -- no, I'm not going to cry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298499,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":299680,"text":"But --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":300855,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":304600,"text":"The thing is that it represents\ninfinite possibility."},{"time":308720,"text":"It represents hope.\nIt represents potential."},{"time":310920,"text":"And what I love about this box,"},{"time":313720,"text":"and what I realize I sort of do\nin whatever it is that I do,"},{"time":318480,"text":"is I find myself\ndrawn to infinite possibility,"},{"time":323480,"text":"that sense of potential."},{"time":324720,"text":"And I realize that mystery\nis the catalyst for imagination."},{"time":327520,"text":"Now, it's not the most\nground-breaking idea,"},{"time":329640,"text":"but when I started to think\nthat maybe there are times"},{"time":332240,"text":"when mystery is more important\nthan knowledge."},{"time":334440,"text":"I started getting interested in this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336280,"text":"And so I started thinking about \"Lost\"\nand the stuff that we do,"},{"time":339320,"text":"and I realized, oh my God, mystery boxes\nare everywhere in what I do!"},{"time":342840,"text":"In the creation of \"Lost,\"\nDamon Lindelof and I,"},{"time":345280,"text":"who created the show with me,"},{"time":346720,"text":"we were basically tasked\nwith creating this series"},{"time":349880,"text":"that we had very little time to do."},{"time":351600,"text":"We had 11 and a half weeks"},{"time":353120,"text":"to write it, cast it, crew it, shoot it,\ncut it, post it, turn in a two-hour pilot."},{"time":357920,"text":"So it was not a lot of time."},{"time":359320,"text":"And that sense of possibility --\nwhat could this thing be?"},{"time":362120,"text":"There was no time to develop it."},{"time":363720,"text":"I'm sure you're all familiar with people"},{"time":365680,"text":"who tell you what you can't do\nand what you should change."},{"time":368440,"text":"There was no time for that,\nwhich is kind of amazing."},{"time":370960,"text":"And so we did this show,"},{"time":372240,"text":"and for those of you\nwho haven't seen it, or don't know it,"},{"time":375040,"text":"I can show you one\nlittle clip from the pilot,"},{"time":377400,"text":"just to show you some stuff that we did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379640,"text":"(Engine roaring)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":388400,"text":"(Video) Claire: Help!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":390360,"text":"Please help me!"},{"time":392560,"text":"Help me! Please, help me!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":396600,"text":"Jack: Get him out of here!\nGet him away from the engine!"},{"time":399400,"text":"Get him out of here!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400688,"text":"(Engine roaring)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406800,"text":"C: Help me, please!\nI'm having contractions!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":410160,"text":"J: How many months pregnant are you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":411920,"text":"C: I'm only eight months."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413400,"text":"J: And how far apart are they coming?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":415240,"text":"C: I don't know. I think it just happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419000,"text":"Man: Hey! Hey! Hey, get away from --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431400,"text":"JJ Abrams: 10 years ago,\nif we wanted to do that,"},{"time":433760,"text":"we'd have to kill a stuntman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440280,"text":"It would be harder."},{"time":442240,"text":"Take two would be a bitch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444880,"text":"So the amazing thing was,\nwe were able to do this thing."},{"time":448000,"text":"And part of that was\nthe amazing availability of technology,"},{"time":450880,"text":"knowing we could do anything."},{"time":452320,"text":"I mean, we could never have done that."},{"time":454200,"text":"We might have been able to write it;"},{"time":455960,"text":"we wouldn't have been able\nto depict it like we did."},{"time":458440,"text":"So part of the amazing thing for me\nis in the creative process,"},{"time":461440,"text":"technology is mind-blowingly\ninspiring to me."},{"time":463600,"text":"I realize that that blank page\nis a magic box, you know?"},{"time":466880,"text":"It needs to be filled\nwith something fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469120,"text":"I used to have the \"Ordinary People\"\nscript that I'd flip through."},{"time":472280,"text":"The romance was amazing to me;\nit would inspire me."},{"time":474720,"text":"I wanted to try and fill pages"},{"time":476200,"text":"with the same kind of spirit\nand thought and emotion"},{"time":480000,"text":"that that script did."},{"time":481240,"text":"So, you know, I love Apple computers."},{"time":483720,"text":"I'm obsessed."},{"time":484960,"text":"So the Apple computer --\nthe PowerBook -- this computer,"},{"time":487680,"text":"it challenges me."},{"time":488920,"text":"It basically says, what are you\ngoing to write worthy of me?"},{"time":491800,"text":"I feel this -- I'm compelled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494840,"text":"And I often am like,\nyou know, dude, today I'm out."},{"time":497280,"text":"I got nothing. You know? So there's that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499440,"text":"In terms of the content of it,"},{"time":500920,"text":"you look at stories, you think,\nwhat are stories but mystery boxes?"},{"time":504120,"text":"There's a fundamental question --\nin TV, the first act is called the teaser."},{"time":507760,"text":"It's literally the teaser.\nIt's the big question."},{"time":510120,"text":"So you're drawn into it.\nThen there's another question."},{"time":512760,"text":"And it goes on. Look at \"Star Wars.\""},{"time":514520,"text":"The droids meet the mysterious woman."},{"time":516360,"text":"Who's that? We don't know. Mystery box!\nThen you meet Luke Skywalker."},{"time":519640,"text":"He gets the droid,\nyou see the holographic image."},{"time":522000,"text":"You learn it's a message.\nShe wants to find Obi Wan Kenobi."},{"time":524840,"text":"He's her only hope.\nBut who's Obi Wan Kenobi?"},{"time":527000,"text":"Mystery box! So then he meets Ben Kenobi."},{"time":528977,"text":"Ben Kenobi is Obi Wan Kenobi.\nHoly shit! So it keeps us --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532760,"text":"Have you guys not seen that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":535200,"text":"It's huge! Anyway --"},{"time":536440,"text":"So there's this thing with mystery boxes\nthat I started feeling compelled."},{"time":542040,"text":"Then there's the thing of mystery\nin terms of imagination --"},{"time":545640,"text":"the withholding of information."},{"time":548160,"text":"You know, doing that intentionally\nis much more engaging."},{"time":552200,"text":"Whether it's like the shark in \"Jaws\" --"},{"time":554160,"text":"if Spielberg's mechanical shark,\nBruce, had worked,"},{"time":556680,"text":"it would not be remotely as scary;\nyou would have seen it too much."},{"time":559880,"text":"In \"Alien\", they never\nreally showed the alien: terrifying!"},{"time":562720,"text":"Even in a movie like\na romantic comedy, \"The Graduate,\""},{"time":565880,"text":"they're having that date,\nand they're in the car,"},{"time":568240,"text":"and it's loud, and so they put the top up."},{"time":570520,"text":"You don't hear anything they're saying!"},{"time":572440,"text":"You can't hear a word!\nBut it's the most romantic date ever."},{"time":575320,"text":"And you love it because you don't hear it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577400,"text":"So to me, there's that.\nAnd then, finally, there's this idea --"},{"time":581000,"text":"stretching the paradigm a little bit --"},{"time":583280,"text":"but the idea of the mystery box."},{"time":585560,"text":"Meaning, what you think you're getting,\nthen what you're really getting."},{"time":589000,"text":"And it's true in so many\nmovies and stories."},{"time":591120,"text":"Look at \"E.T.,\" for example --"},{"time":592600,"text":"\"E.T.\" is this unbelievable\nmovie about what?"},{"time":594760,"text":"It's about an alien\nwho meets a kid, right?"},{"time":596800,"text":"Well, it's not. \"E.T.\" is about divorce."},{"time":598760,"text":"\"E.T.\" is about a heartbroken,\ndivorce-crippled family,"},{"time":601400,"text":"and ultimately,\nthis kid who can't find his way."},{"time":603680,"text":"\"Die Hard,\" right? Crazy, great, fun,\naction-adventure movie in a building."},{"time":607240,"text":"It's about a guy\nwho's on the verge of divorce."},{"time":609480,"text":"He's showing up to L.A.,\ntail between his legs."},{"time":611720,"text":"There are great scenes --"},{"time":612960,"text":"maybe not the most amazing\ndramatic scenes in the history of time,"},{"time":616120,"text":"but pretty great scenes."},{"time":617360,"text":"There's a half an hour\nof investment in character"},{"time":619720,"text":"before you get to the stuff\nthat you're expecting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622120,"text":"When you look at a movie like \"Jaws,\""},{"time":623960,"text":"the scene that you expect --\nwe have the screen?"},{"time":626240,"text":"These are the kind of scenes"},{"time":627640,"text":"that you remember and expect from \"Jaws.\""},{"time":630120,"text":"And she's being eaten;"},{"time":632240,"text":"there's a shark."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633560,"text":"(Woman screaming)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":634800,"text":"The thing about \"Jaws\" is,\nit's really about a guy"},{"time":637200,"text":"who is sort of dealing with his place\nin the world -- with his masculinity,"},{"time":640760,"text":"with his family, how he's going to,\nyou know, make it work in this new town."},{"time":644360,"text":"This is one of my favorite scenes ever,"},{"time":646280,"text":"and this is a scene\nthat you wouldn't necessarily think of"},{"time":649040,"text":"when you think of \"Jaws.\"\nBut it's an amazing scene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706640,"text":"(Video) Father: C'mere."},{"time":711440,"text":"Give us a kiss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713400,"text":"Son: Why?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":716680,"text":"Father: 'Cause I need it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718720,"text":"JJA: Come on. \"Why? 'Cause I need it\"?"},{"time":720554,"text":"Best scene ever, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":721820,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":722860,"text":"Come on! So you think of \"Jaws\" --"},{"time":724680,"text":"so that's the kind of stuff that,"},{"time":726320,"text":"like, you know --\nthe investment of character,"},{"time":729280,"text":"which is the stuff that really\nis inside the box, you know?"},{"time":732080,"text":"It's why when people do sequels,\nor rip off movies, you know, of a genre,"},{"time":735560,"text":"they're ripping off the wrong thing."},{"time":737320,"text":"You're not supposed\nto rip off the shark or the monster."},{"time":740000,"text":"You know, if you rip something off --\nrip off the character."},{"time":742880,"text":"Rip off the stuff that matters."},{"time":744440,"text":"I mean, look inside yourself\nand figure out what is inside you."},{"time":747440,"text":"Because ultimately,\nthe mystery box is all of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749920,"text":"So there's that. Then the distribution."},{"time":751802,"text":"What's a bigger mystery box\nthan a movie theater? You know?"},{"time":754640,"text":"You go to the theater,\nyou're just so excited to see anything."},{"time":757600,"text":"The moment the lights go down\nis often the best part."},{"time":760120,"text":"And you're full of that amazing --\nthat feeling of excited anticipation."},{"time":764600,"text":"And often, the movie's there\nand it's going,"},{"time":766720,"text":"and then something happens\nand you go, \"Oh --\", and then, \"Mmm ...\""},{"time":769920,"text":"When it's a great movie,\nyou're along for the ride"},{"time":772320,"text":"because you're willing\nto give yourself to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774487,"text":"So to me, whether it's a TV,\nan iPod, computer, cell phone --"},{"time":778320,"text":"It's funny, I'm an --\nas I said, Apple fanatic --"},{"time":780680,"text":"and one day, about a year or so ago,"},{"time":782440,"text":"I was signing on online in the morning\nto watch Steve Jobs' keynote,"},{"time":786160,"text":"because I always do."},{"time":787400,"text":"And he came on,\nhe was presenting the video iPod,"},{"time":790560,"text":"and what was on\nthe enormous iPod behind him?"},{"time":793360,"text":"\"Lost\"! I had no idea!"},{"time":795680,"text":"And I realized, holy shit,\nit'd come full circle."},{"time":798040,"text":"The inspiration I get from the technology"},{"time":800017,"text":"is now using the stuff that I do\nto sell technology. It's nuts!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":803000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":804240,"text":"I was going to show you a couple\nof other things I'm going to skip."},{"time":807520,"text":"I'll show you one other thing\nthat has nothing to do with anything."},{"time":810720,"text":"This is something online;\nsix years ago, they did this."},{"time":813380,"text":"This is an online thing done by guys\nwho had some visual effects experience."},{"time":816980,"text":"But the point was,\nthat they were doing things"},{"time":819180,"text":"that were using these mystery boxes\nthat they had -- everyone has now."},{"time":822500,"text":"What I've realized is what my grandfather\ndid for me when I was a kid,"},{"time":825860,"text":"everyone has access to now."},{"time":827680,"text":"You don't need to have my grandfather,\nthough you wish you had."},{"time":830680,"text":"But I have to tell you --"},{"time":831960,"text":"this is a guy doing stuff\non a Quadra 950 computer --"},{"time":834480,"text":"the resolution's a little bit low --"},{"time":836240,"text":"using Infinity software\nthey stopped making 15 years ago."},{"time":838960,"text":"He's doing stuff that looks as amazing"},{"time":840840,"text":"as stuff I've seen\nreleased from Hollywood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":844040,"text":"The most incredible\nsort of mystery, I think,"},{"time":847040,"text":"is now the question of what comes next."},{"time":849800,"text":"Because it is now democratized."},{"time":851840,"text":"So now, the creation of media --\nit's everywhere."},{"time":854360,"text":"The stuff that I was lucky\nand begging for to get when I was a kid"},{"time":858200,"text":"is now ubiquitous."},{"time":859440,"text":"And so, there's an amazing sense\nof opportunity out there."},{"time":862280,"text":"And when I think of the filmmakers\nwho exist out there now"},{"time":865400,"text":"who would have been silenced, you know --"},{"time":867400,"text":"who have been silenced in the past --"},{"time":869840,"text":"it's a very exciting thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871200,"text":"I used to say in classes\nand lectures and stuff,"},{"time":874360,"text":"to someone who wants to write,\n\"Go! Write! Do your thing.\""},{"time":877120,"text":"It's free, you don't need permission."},{"time":878920,"text":"But now I can say, \"Go make your movie!\"\nThere's nothing stopping you"},{"time":882200,"text":"from going out there\nand getting the technology."},{"time":884480,"text":"You can lease, rent,\nbuy stuff off the shelf"},{"time":886920,"text":"that is either as good, or just as good,"},{"time":890720,"text":"as the stuff that's being used\nby the, you know, \"legit people.\""},{"time":894280,"text":"No community is best served\nwhen only the elite have control."},{"time":898440,"text":"And I feel like\nthis is an amazing opportunity"},{"time":900640,"text":"to see what else is out there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":902120,"text":"When I did \"Mission: Impossible III,\"\nwe had amazing visual effects."},{"time":905360,"text":"ILM did the effects; it was incredible."},{"time":907280,"text":"And sort of my dream to be involved."},{"time":909040,"text":"And there are a couple\nof sequences in the movie,"},{"time":911400,"text":"like these couple of moments\nI'll show you."},{"time":918520,"text":"There's that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926480,"text":"(Video) Luther: Ethan, move!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":932840,"text":"(Explosion)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":940520,"text":"Obviously, I have an obsession\nwith big crazy explosions."},{"time":943400,"text":"So my favorite visual effect in the movie\nis the one I'm about to show you."},{"time":947000,"text":"It's a scene in which\nTom's character wakes up."},{"time":949240,"text":"He's drowsy. He's crazy."},{"time":950520,"text":"And the guy wakes up,\nand he shoves this gun in his nose"},{"time":953200,"text":"and shoots this little capsule\ninto his brain"},{"time":955360,"text":"that he's going to use later\nto kill him, as bad guys do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":964240,"text":"(Video) Brownway: Good morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":967680,"text":"JJA: OK, now."},{"time":968960,"text":"When we shot that scene,"},{"time":970200,"text":"the actor who had the gun,\nan English actor, Eddie Marsan --"},{"time":973280,"text":"sweetheart, great guy --"},{"time":974520,"text":"he kept taking the gun\nand putting it into Tom's nose,"},{"time":977120,"text":"and it was hurting Tom's nose."},{"time":978640,"text":"And I learned this\nvery early on in my career:"},{"time":980840,"text":"Don't hurt Tom's nose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":982120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":984040,"text":"There are three things\nyou don't want to do."},{"time":986160,"text":"Number two is: Don't hurt Tom's nose."},{"time":988000,"text":"So Eddie has this gun --\nand he's this sweet English guy."},{"time":990720,"text":"He's like, \"Sorry,\nI don't want to hurt you.\""},{"time":992880,"text":"I'm like, \"We have to\nmake this look good.\""},{"time":994920,"text":"And I realized that we had to do something\nbecause it wasn't working."},{"time":998183,"text":"And I thought back\nto what I would have done"},{"time":1000440,"text":"using the Super 8 camera\nthat my grandfather got me"},{"time":1002880,"text":"sitting in that room,"},{"time":1004120,"text":"and I realized that hand\ndidn't have to be Eddie Marsan's."},{"time":1006880,"text":"It could be Tom's."},{"time":1008120,"text":"And Tom would know\njust how hard to push the gun."},{"time":1010480,"text":"He wouldn't hurt himself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1011720,"text":"So we took his hand and we painted it\nto look a little bit more like Eddie's."},{"time":1015400,"text":"We put it in Eddie's sleeve,"},{"time":1017280,"text":"and so the hand that you see --"},{"time":1018800,"text":"that's not Eddie's hand, that's Tom's.\nSo Tom is playing two roles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1022000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1023440,"text":"And he didn't ask for any more money."},{"time":1025280,"text":"So here, here. Watch it again."},{"time":1027839,"text":"There he is. He's waking up."},{"time":1029359,"text":"He's drowsy, been through a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035400,"text":"(Video) Brownway: Good morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1037000,"text":"JJA: Tom's hand. Tom's hand. Tom's hand."},{"time":1039160,"text":"Anyway."},{"time":1040400,"text":"So ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1041640,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1045040,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1048359,"text":"So you don't need the greatest technology\nto do things that can work in movies."},{"time":1053000,"text":"And the mystery box,\nin honor of my grandfather, stays closed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1056360,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1057600,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}